{"tid":220859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林鄭組班】陳美齡東京6億日元豪宅曝光！ 4層高擁7房兼有電梯","createTime":"2017-04-28T09:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T14:31:02.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7d6ffbac33e46752221b02fc75909fd97b2646","tid":220859,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"【林鄭組班】陳美齡東京6億日元豪宅曝光！ 4層高擁7房兼有電梯<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去年再獲聯合國兒童基金會（UNICEF）委任為「東亞及太平洋地區大使」的陳美齡，經常公開呼籲日本人捐款救助各地不幸兒童。不過，她近年多次在其價值6億日元的豪宅內高調接受媒體訪問，就被當地人批評她一邊炫富一邊叫人做慈善，表現偽善。</span><br />\n<br />\n日本一個綜藝節目2015年曾介紹過陳美齡位於東京澀谷高級住宅區廣尾町的4層高豪宅，該幢豪宅樓齡至今有22年，除了客飯廳和廚房，有多達7間房間，甚至設有室內升降機方便上落。豪宅面積達60疊，即近1,100平方呎，當時市價要約6億日元，折合港幣逾4,000萬元。<br />\n<br />\n節目所見，豪宅全屋舖設白色大理石地磚，裝潢極具歐洲古典風格，不少傢俬都是意大利出品，金碧輝煌，據稱單是傢俬已價值超過1億日元。她更展示在豪宅內開派對招呼過首相安倍晉三的相片，其中一個房屋內設有一個大型玻璃書櫃，展示她過去30多年演藝生涯所獲得的獎項。<br />\n<br />\n雖然陳美齡稱豪宅同時會充當事務所，不過節目播出後，屋內的豪華光景依然惹來外界眼紅。不少日本網民揶揄陳美齡居於「宮殿」，更有人改圖稱若自己都住在皇宮裡當然也樂於捐助窮苦兒童。<br />\n<br />\n近年不斷有網民質疑由陳美齡擔任大使的「日本聯合國國際兒童緊急基金協會」（日本UNICEF）會從募集到的捐款先扣掉約20%作為活動資金，餘款才會匯到UNICEF總部，但日本著名女主持人黑柳徹子其實才是獲UNICEF委任的國際親善大使，黑柳的募款帳戶更會將所有捐款直接匯給UNICEF，質疑若要捐款直接捐給黑柳更好。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493368403_c471.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493368403_c471.jpg&h=44f5f1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56625703&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56625703%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=3ca14f14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170428%26guid%3D56625703%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=fc313d5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170428&amp;guid=56625703&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"a2e85d69518ed88868049224906180bd0712d2b7","tid":220859,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:20:21.000Z","msg":"更展示在豪宅內開派對招呼過<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>首相安倍晉三</strong></span>的相片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n漢奸，走狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8e9d99cf8356a8f5855a681498f89b309e13e7","tid":220859,"uid":85163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4d71fe6dc67ee25cfef0c95706fd32b75b82bd4","tid":220859,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493368439_fe24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493368439_fe24.jpg&h=273db834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳美齡的4層高豪宅更設有室內升降機。(電視畫面)<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170428/large/1493368851_10ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170428%2Flarge%2F1493368851_10ab.jpg&h=16278b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳美齡曾在豪宅內設宴款待日本首相安倍晉三。(電視畫面)"},{"pid":"a2bc874fc5d23f6c1e2f1b6e83a7c88b7bf0906f","tid":220859,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"講一套做一套"},{"pid":"187423a3a79dc9293472b195fab5e57c99a22490","tid":220859,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"日本藝能最"},{"pid":"3d7b946b07ec9ba3bc60fce3c0fbd49c6516ea66","tid":220859,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"日本藝能最豪第2位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk